# ============================================================================
# WHAT GETS COMMITTED
# ============================================================================

# ✅ All .py files (core logic)
# ✅ README.md
# ✅ ARCHITECTURE_DIAGRAM.md
# ✅ config/ directory
# ✅ requirements.txt
# ✅ setup_venv.sh & run_weex_test.sh
# ✅ templates/ (for dashboard)
#
# ❌ .env (credentials)
# ❌ logs/ (trading data)
# ❌ venv/ (virtual environment)
# ❌ All other .md files
# ❌ Most .sh files
# ❌ Sensitive/temporary files
